graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:CommonCreateAttachmentLibraryInput!)
{
	commonCreateAttachmentLibrary (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		filename
		originFilename
		mimetype
		extension
		relativePathSegments
		width
		height
		size
		url
		meta
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	commonGetAttachmentLibraries (query: $query)
	{
		id
		filename
		originFilename
		mimetype
		extension
		relativePathSegments
		width
		height
		size
		url
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
